title: This guy has can beatbox dubstep with a McDonald's cup and we're lovin' it
text:
We swear McDonald's didn't pay us to say that.
What we can't be sure of however is whether or not the big McD paid Parker Kane for his beatboxing skills and this performance with a McDonald's straw and cup. If they didn't, we hope he gets at least a free meal out of it seeing as he's gone viral with his dubstep skills.
Via YouTube
